Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.36,0:00:12.80,DTB-Default,Man,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.23,0:00:16.18,DTB-Default,Man,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:18.33,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,It's always raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:20.88,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,What a miserable country.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:23.75,DTB-Default,Man,0,0,0,,Are you the one who called me out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:35.97,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,You already know why you deserve this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.86,0:00:38.16,DTB-Default,Ukiyama,0,0,0,,Well, just give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.39,0:01:52.51,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,What an unpleasant season.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.51,0:01:54.36,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Damp and stagnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:58.83,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Well, it sure fits the image of this grimy town.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.23,0:02:02.66,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,My name is Kurasawa Gai,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:04.91,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,private investigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:10.74,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I've been making a living by observing the damp, stagnant nature of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.76,0:02:14.88,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I don't trust anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.41,0:02:17.97,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,My only love is tobacco.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.71,0:02:24.35,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,It stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:34.46,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "funyuu",
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:36.52,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,you flat-chested girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:39.11,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.48,0:02:42.27,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Those kinds of insensitive remarks could be considered sexual harassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:44.18,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,This is the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.73,0:02:47.16,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,The stench of tobacco, athlete's foot medication,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:49.25,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,and something else mixed in for good measure...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:52.05,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Yeah, the smell of my armpits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:53.23,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Drop dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:56.67,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Hey, this isn't the time to be slacking off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:03:01.04,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,The TV station came to collect the subscription fee yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:03.47,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,They'll really block the feed these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:05.86,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,You can still see network stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.86,0:03:07.70,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,I can't miss Bara no Maurice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:09.46,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,An anime?
Comment: 0,0:03:08.49,0:03:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:13.43,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Why are you watching anime at work in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:17.57,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Wasn't that part of the conditions we agreed upon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:21.61,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be working in a dump like this if it wasn't for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:23.29,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:33.75,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:35.27,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,It's a woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:36.90,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,and a beauty at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:38.68,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:41.08,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Investigator's intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:44.28,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,How many times have you gotten in trouble because of that intuition?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:46.93,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Don't be deceived, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:49.12,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I don't care if I'm deceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:50.98,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,No, more than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:54.14,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I want to be deceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:59.15,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,So this is a genuine request?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:01.63,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Um, what else would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:04.64,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Well, debt collectors, for example...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:05.56,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.61,0:04:09.91,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,A search for a missing cat, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:16.13,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Yes. My husband Yuzuki and I loved her as if she was our own child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:21.53,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,If Mii-chan were gone, it would cause Yuzuki grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:24.32,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,So you haven't told your husband yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:26.74,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:29.18,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,My husband passed away quite some time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:31.54,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry about your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:35.81,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Although I understand your feelings and the circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:37.58,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,If it was only a search for a missing person
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:39.92,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,instead of a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:42.14,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,It was disrespectful of me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:44.79,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,to ask a private detective about something of this nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:47.15,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,No, it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:51.82,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Maybe a dog, but a cat is somewhat out of my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:54.10,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,How about five hundred thousand yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:59.55,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,I'll pay half in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:04.06,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,You don't have to return the money, even if she isn't found.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:06.89,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,No, that's not the issue...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.71,0:05:09.89,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,We'll find Mii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.77,0:05:13.90,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,You... Who said I'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:17.79,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Leave it to the Kurasawa Detective Agency!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:21.78,DTB-Default,Tai Ming,0,0,0,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:24.82,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:28.60,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Competitive eating contest or something? Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:30.62,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Yeah. I can't believe
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:31.97,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,you don't like cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.98,0:05:36.41,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,First of all, you're not in a position to be picky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:44.36,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Huh? "Former cosmetics employee falls to his death"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:47.76,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Something like this happened the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.76,0:05:51.78,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,"The police are still investigating on the premise of a suicide."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:55.92,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,We have to make a missing cat poster, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:06:01.37,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,We need to distribute fliers and trick local kids into looking for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:04.09,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,There are tons of things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:05.74,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,It's the same company, as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:09.10,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Isn't it suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:10.94,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Were you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.94,0:06:12.83,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Consecutive suicides, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:15.33,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,They were both former employees of Fiore Cosmetics.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:17.19,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Fiore Cosmetics?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:17.92,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:21.86,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Oh, I just remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:25.45,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,That perfume... It's the really expensive one from Fiore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:28.41,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,The widow who was looking for the cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:31.25,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,You could smell it a mile away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:33.98,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I sure remember that scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:36.77,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,No, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:40.80,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,More importantly, there are things we need to do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:42.81,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:44.51,DTB-Default,Tai Ming,0,0,0,,Thanks, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:54.32,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Hey, did you get a look at that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:55.87,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Are you talking about that glutton?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:59.29,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,He'll definitely get fat after he turns thirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.70,0:07:02.59,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,He's hot! He's cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:05.30,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Especially around the collar bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:10.78,DTB-Default,Rika,0,0,0,,Is it tasty, Hernandez?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:13.47,DTB-Default,Tai Ming,0,0,0,,Rika, where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:15.91,DTB-Default,Tai Ming,0,0,0,,I'm busy. Where the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:17.38,DTB-Default,Rika,0,0,0,,Bye, Hernandez!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:20.77,DTB-Default,Rika,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:27.21,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Is it any good?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:29.59,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Well, I can't let good intentions go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:34.03,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,What did you want to talk to me about, Hernandez?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:40.54,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,This one is pretty close,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:43.84,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,but the nose is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:46.04,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,The nose isn't black.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:48.55,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Sorry, but here's a reward for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:51.42,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Onee-chan's cosplay picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:53.43,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Here. Thanks, nyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:54.93,DTB-Default,Kids,0,0,0,,I don't want this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.93,0:07:58.77,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Hey, where were you while I was diligently looking for the cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:02.29,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,That's a job for women and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:05.81,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Those kinds of discriminative remarks aren't politically correct these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:07.88,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,I bet you're just afraid of cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:19.40,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I found out about something interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:24.24,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,That widow's deceased husband was an executive of Fiore Cosmetics.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:25.27,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:29.24,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,The consecutive suicides were committed by former employees of the same cosmetic company.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:31.84,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Don't you think the pieces are starting to fit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:33.36,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:34.82,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,You're an idiot, Kiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:41.62,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Discovering clues from subtle connections is part of what being a detective is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:43.25,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,A man's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:47.81,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Hi, boys and girls! Can you show your cats to Onee-chan, nya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:49.50,DTB-Default,Kids,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:52.52,Title,,0,0,0,,Episode Seven The Scent of Gardenias Lingers in the Summer Rain... (Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:06.40,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,A gardenia, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:10.62,DTB-Default,Maid,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:12.65,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,It's Kurasawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:18.17,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Um, I have an appointment with the madam...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.85,0:09:23.42,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,today, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:26.42,DTB-Default,Maid,0,0,0,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:39.44,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,It looks more like a grandfather and his granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:43.03,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I bet you overexerted yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:09:57.14,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Does it smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:10:00.87,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,I apologize for making you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:03.50,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,N-No, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:06.76,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,You have a wonderful collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.22,0:10:10.34,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Oh, the perfume?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:12.47,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,It was Yuzuki's hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.47,0:10:17.60,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Oh, your late husband, Yuzuki Sakutarou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:20.48,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I heard he was an executive of Fiore Cosmetics,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.21,0:10:24.48,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,who started his career as a perfumer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:25.36,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Is that why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:28.33,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,He was sensitive to fragrances.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.38,0:10:31.62,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,As expected of a detective,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:33.65,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,you've deducted nearly everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:36.32,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,No, this was nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:40.14,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,My, how surprising, Chanel-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:42.12,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,for you to sit on the lap of a stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:43.84,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Chanel-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:47.88,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,You like cats, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:50.46,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Yes, I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:10:59.27,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I pissed my pants a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:24.08,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:26.02,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I made a wrong turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:29.39,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Huh? You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:35.05,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,A part-time worker?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:37.69,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Yes, to sort the bookshelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:38.77,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Is he an acquaintance of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:41.48,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:45.02,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,What about Mii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:48.86,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. She hasn't been found yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.86,0:11:50.22,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:53.10,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, madam...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:56.57,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I mean... There are several things I'd like to inquire about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:57.20,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:12:01.30,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Perhaps... it was Toshiko's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:02.72,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,No, it probably was Toshiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:04.29,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,T-Toshiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:09.09,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,You already knew I was his second wife, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:10.38,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:15.42,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Have you also heard the story about how I took Yuzuki away from his first wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:17.01,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:21.39,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,It's all right. Those rumors were bound to be exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:24.91,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,I wonder who was the one who actually took anything away, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.31,0:12:27.68,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,A huge amount of consolation money, the mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:30.32,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,and Mii-chan, to top it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:32.49,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Hold it right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:35.27,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Are you saying that his ex-wife took the cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:36.32,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,It must be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:39.70,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Mr. Detective, conduct a search of Toshiko's mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:40.20,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:43.58,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,She's an anti-social person who lives alone in that mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:45.68,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,I hear she's frequently away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:46.95,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:50.53,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Mr. Detective, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:51.95,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:53.63,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Mr. Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:54.72,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:58.22,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,You have some wax in your ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.34,0:13:12.80,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,You mustn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:15.65,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Hold still and don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:21.41,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Madam! Madam!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:24.16,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,My, what waxy ears you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:28.37,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Sorry for making you do this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:32.13,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'm doing it because I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:35.28,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:37.62,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I've never experienced such wonderful ear cleaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:41.05,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,You're exaggerating. It's been a hobby of mine for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:43.64,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, do you know what they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:46.23,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,People with waxy ears have strong body odor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:49.14,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Isn't that an old wives' tale?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:52.33,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Is that so? How about yourself, Mr. Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:53.15,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Hey, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:56.72,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,G-Give me a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:13:59.96,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,As I thought! I have waxy ears, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:04.27,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Yuzuki wasn't pleased with that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.27,0:14:06.03,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,which is why I started wearing stronger perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:08.54,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Does that bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:10.87,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,No, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:13.29,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,But this scent...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:15.55,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,is like a gardenia, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.03,0:14:19.52,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,Yuzuki told me it fit the present season.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:23.85,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,To be honest, I never liked strong perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:28.36,DTB-Default,Arisa,0,0,0,,I guess I was completely persuaded by Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:35.63,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:38.49,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I heard you work part-time at the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:41.76,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,This is my business card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:44.24,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I saw you earlier at a ramen shop in the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.24,0:14:45.97,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,That's why I asked about you.
Comment: 0,0:14:44.33,0:20:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.16,0:14:49.30,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.15,0:14:52.71,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,A coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.71,0:14:54.88,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:58.30,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,A man working part-time as if he was waiting for an opportunity like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:00.48,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,A beautiful widow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:01.88,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,A suspicious maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:05.63,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,There's definitely something going on in that mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.56,0:15:07.60,DTB-Default,Driver,0,0,0,,Are you getting on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:08.38,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:10.80,DTB-Default,Driver,0,0,0,,Are you going to get on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:12.63,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:15.77,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Why are you suddenly interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:17.94,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,It's work, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:21.70,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,It's a crime to sneak into other people's homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:24.32,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Don't make it sound like an appalling thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:27.29,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I'm just going to look for a cat while the tenant is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.29,0:15:29.36,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,That's definitely a crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:31.12,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Well, I don't really care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:34.63,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,For your information, I'm on paid vacation starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:40.25,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,I already told you I had an important event to attend at Aoto tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:42.78,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Are you saying that I'll have to look for the cat by myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:44.47,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:47.46,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,It's work, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:52.39,DTB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Is he around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.39,0:15:56.01,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Yin was only able to track him up to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:00.79,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:24.08,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Is that the remuneration for your contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:25.71,DTB-Default,Man,0,0,0,,A cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.92,0:16:38.58,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,A homicide disguised as a suicide, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:40.18,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,What an elaborate plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:44.22,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:55.04,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Why did you interfere?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:16:57.02,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:17:00.28,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,He was about to possess you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.28,0:17:01.55,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Possess?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.55,0:17:03.39,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Your body, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:06.01,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,He has the same ability as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.01,0:17:08.33,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,The possession of other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:10.51,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Although I can only do it to animals,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:12.58,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,he can move from person to person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:18.88,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Geez, why does the weather have to be so hot when the sun's out, for once?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:31.20,DTB-Default,Waitress,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:35.08,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Toshiko-chan's not home, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:38.18,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I don't know whether that's a good thing or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:39.27,DTB-Default,Waitress,0,0,0,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:40.08,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:42.55,DTB-Default,Waitress,0,0,0,,Your order, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:44.31,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Oh, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:47.88,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:50.86,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.14,0:17:57.31,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Forgot something... Forgot something...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:17:59.23,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Forgot something...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.23,0:18:03.23,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Forgot something... Forgot something, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:05.71,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Scary guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:10.74,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,It's him. What's he doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:23.04,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:26.62,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Mao, we have company.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:28.72,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Don't lose sight of the contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.72,0:18:30.26,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Mao, do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:31.52,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Mao?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:37.30,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Why was that guy here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.73,0:18:41.27,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Does he know about the connection between the widow and the ex-wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:47.92,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Regardless of everything, Toshiko-chan's house sure is huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:51.39,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,What is this smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.39,0:18:53.24,DTB-Default,Neighbor,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.62,0:18:56.58,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm not a suspicious person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:18:58.54,DTB-Default,Neighbor,0,0,0,,Nice shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.54,0:18:59.40,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:02.14,DTB-Default,Neighbor,0,0,0,,Do you know the person who lives over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:03.47,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:05.13,DTB-Default,Neighbor,0,0,0,,You don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:08.86,DTB-Default,Neighbor,0,0,0,,That house is causing problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:10.09,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.09,0:19:12.89,DTB-Default,Neighbor,0,0,0,,It's that, the garbage mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.89,0:19:14.90,DTB-Default,Neighbor,0,0,0,,I've been complaining to the ward office,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:17.18,DTB-Default,Neighbor,0,0,0,,but they aren't handling it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:20.56,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Garbage mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:20.56,DTB-Default,Neighbor,0,0,0,,{\an8}Fore!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:23.14,DTB-Default,Waitress,0,0,0,,That'll be four hundred and twenty yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:28.44,DTB-Default,Man,0,0,0,,This isn't my jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.17,0:19:30.07,DTB-Default,Man,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.49,0:19:35.57,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,This looks pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:42.91,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,How careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.44,0:19:51.76,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:54.79,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Geez, why are things like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.76,0:19:57.88,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:14.99,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Damn! Outsmarted by a stupid cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:23.71,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:43.46,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Literally written as "the rain in May" in kanji, its meaning is "early summer rain".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.46,0:20:45.82,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,The cold rain seeps into my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:49.07,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,The sweet fragrance of the gardenia tickles my nostrils.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:51.41,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Widow... The sweet sound of the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:53.45,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Oh, why must you be a widow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:20:56.80,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Every time I recall your superb ear-cleaning skills, my heart goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:20:58.92,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:21:01.33,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,If you're seduced by that woman's pheromones,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.33,0:21:03.64,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,she's going to take everything you have, right down to the hairs on your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.19,0:21:08.66,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Even a girl like you shouldn't say something like that out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:09.33,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,566)}Episode Eight The Scent of Gardenias Lingers in the Summer Rain... (Part Two)